 
<p>
The Tories are so determined to be cruel to refugees that they pushed ahead
with deportation to Rwanda despite 
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2022/jul/19/uk-officials-raised-concerns-over-rwanda-policy-documents-show">knowing many reasons they should not.</a>
<p>
They are also determined to do it before a court rules on whether it
is 
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2022/jul/03/uk-home-office-plans-second-flight-to-deport-asylum-seekers-to-rwanda">lawful in the first place.<a/>
<p>
Thus, it's not just some refugees they plan to do wrong to -- it's
every citizen of the UK.

 